About us

The Gym Pod

The Gym Pod is Singaporeâ€™s first 24/7, pay-per-use private gym. The Gym Pod also has other offerings such as The Flow Pod, The Grit Pod, The Rumble Pod and The Spin Pod. With a Smart Mirror, The Gym Pod provides workout videos to guide customers of beginner, intermediate and advanced levels to maximize their workout.

All users of The Gym Pod have to submit their vaccination records via the app. Yes, even your invited guests. If you face issues submitting your vaccination records, please contact support@thegympod.com

The Gym Pod @ Bukit Merah Central

Bukit Merah Central has a community of healthy residents and hard-working professionals. The Gym Pod @ Bukit Merah Central provides working professionals an avenue to exercise before and after work, or even during their lunchtime. The private gym helps local residents achieve a healthier lifestyle.
